{"tid":2439817,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曱甴狂迷｜23歲少年高峯期飼養逾千隻曱甴 徒手捉小強上身任爬：佢哋好靚好可愛","createTime":"2021-03-09T13:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T13:32:13.000Z","uid":379267,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0f982ec1e8828094fc2b401b36b9fae4bace26f8","tid":2439817,"uid":379267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:32:13.000Z","msg":"蟑螂，一種體形細小卻足以令人驚慌逃跑的生物。大眾對牠們避之則吉，但在23歲的Lu Els（化名）眼中，牠們卻是人間瑰寶。Lu Els飼養蟑螂近10年，接觸過百多個物種，自小情迷蟑螂的他說：「只因蟑螂太美麗。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLu Els現時與家人同住，過往亦曾因為蟑螂們與家人爭執。他說：「家人的反應是你不要養這些蟑螂，很骯髒，養來又沒用。現在還會有怨言的，只不過有時是習慣了，怨言少了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210305/7CXMWL4JRJGI5LMCEB7WQMLXJI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210305%2F7CXMWL4JRJGI5LMCEB7WQMLXJI%2F&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1Mhy5vkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=6442f18b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20210305%2F7CXMWL4JRJGI5LMCEB7WQMLXJI%2F&h=4b5c4669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20210305/7CXMWL4JRJGI5LMCEB7WQMLXJI/</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/stRfmTG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FstRfmTG.png&h=84bef0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gwi5J61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGwi5J61.png&h=bac2573e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Okf7Xr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkf7Xr1.png&h=2dfb7347&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}